@startuml
!include common-sequence.iuml

title deploy-shared-layer\n(GitHub Action → CloudFormation)

actor "GitHub Actions Runner" as GHA

box "AWS" #ffdbbb
    participant "CloudFormation / SAM" as CF
    participant "Lambda" as Lambda
    collections "S3\n(SAM artifacts)" as S3
end box

GHA -> GHA : SAM build\ntemplate: lambdas/shared/template.yaml\nPackages: logging_config.py,\napp_config.py, feature_flags.py
GHA -> S3 : Upload layer artifact
S3 --> GHA : Artifact uploaded

GHA -> CF++ : SAM deploy\nstack: firefly-shared-layer
CF -> Lambda++ : Publish Lambda layer version\n(Python shared modules)
Lambda --> CF-- : LayerVersionArn
CF --> GHA-- : CREATE_COMPLETE / UPDATE_COMPLETE\nOutput: LayerVersionArn

alt SAM build fails (Python dependency issue)
    GHA --> GHA : Build error
    note over GHA : Workflow fails before any AWS changes.\nFix Python dependencies and re-run.
end

alt Stack creation/update fails
    CF --> GHA : ROLLBACK_COMPLETE
    note over GHA : Workflow fails with exit code != 0
end

@enduml
